<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="early-adv">early <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɜːli/    美 /'ɜːrli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>早；提早；在早期；在初期：</strong></h4>
<p>反 late </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Early to bed and early to rise makes a man healthy, wealthy and wise. 
睡得早，起得早，富裕、聪明、身体好。</p><footer>——富兰克林</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The next day, we set off <strong>early in the morning</strong>.
第二天，我们一大早就出发了。</p><footer>2008 北京书面表达</footer></div></div>